  "text": "HyProb-Ontology [CITATION_1] is a framework that enhances the data input and reasoning processes of its predecessors. Instead of using ordinary BNs, HyProb-Ontology uses a hybrid BN that incorporates BNs for probabilistic reasoning on discrete variables and conditional Gaussian fuzzification for probabilistic reasoning on continuous variables. There is no significant improvement other than these.",
